(17, 'Winter Vacation 2012', 'Hello there.  I am in Virginia visiting my family for Christmas and New Year''s Day.  I''ll be back in Florida after the holidays.  While I''m on vacation, I am learning how to create blog sites using Wordpress.  I think Wordpress is awesome. I can''t wait to build and update sites in Wordpress.\n\nMy hard drive on my MacBook Pro failed on me.  Luckily, I still have this laptop under warranty so I went to the Apple Store in Greensboro, North Carolina to have it replaced immediately.  Unfortunatly, everything in my hard drive is gone.  But thank goodness I backed up most of my work on my external hard drive.  \n\nAnyway, I wish all of you a safe and happy holiday.  Hopefully there are good things to come in 2012.\n\nFranco', '2011-12-29 12:33:47', 1, 0, 'December 29, 2011, 8:33 pm'),
